Template images bundled under assets/templates/ are widely-circulated
internet meme templates, included at reduced resolution for the purpose of
meme creation under a fair-use posture. Provenance for each template is
recorded in the "source" field of assets/templates/manifest.json.

If you are a rights holder and would like a template removed, please open an
issue and it will be removed promptly.

